        <para>
            <emph type="boldundersc">WIRING INFORMATION</emph>
        </para>
        <para>This feature is software driven.</para>
        <para>
            <emph type="boldundersc">TESTING</emph>
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Start vehicle and make sure the parking brake is engaged.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Turn the windshield wipers on any setting except for the slowest intermittent speed.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Leave the wipers on this setting for 60 seconds without adjusting the wiper speed.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">After 60 seconds, the wipers should slow to the lowest speed.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Adjust the wiper speed control.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The wiper setting should match the user set speed.</para>
        </step1>
        <para>
            <emph type="boldundersc">HOW TO ADD THESE FEATURES:</emph>
        </para>
        <para>Use the Diamond Logic&#174; Builder software to install the appropriate software and determine correct
            settings for programmable parameters.
        </para>
